# 🚀 UGC Ad Content Pack (Prompt Engineering Task 2)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is part of **Future Interns – Prompt Engineering Task 2 (2026)**.

The goal is to create a **high-converting UGC (User Generated Content) Ad System** using AI tools like ChatGPT, capable of generating:

- UGC-style ad scripts  
- Multiple hooks  
- Call-To-Actions (CTAs)  
- Instagram-ready captions  

These ads are designed to feel **natural, authentic, and relatable**, just like real customer reviews.

---

## 🏷️ Chosen Business
**GlowUp Beauty Salon (Local Business – Bhimavaram)**  

### 🎯 Target Audience:
- Women (18–35)
- Interested in skincare & beauty services  
- Looking for affordable and trustworthy salons  

---

## ❗ Problem
Many people:
- Spend too much on expensive salons  
- Don’t get expected results  
- Don’t trust local salons  

---

## 💡 Solution
GlowUp Beauty Salon provides:
- Affordable pricing  
- Professional services  
- Visible results  

This UGC content builds **trust + relatability**, increasing conversions.

